<h2>Pool Houses</h2>
A pool house (also known as a pool cabana) is an alternative to a pool enclosure, it is generally a small structure that sit near the pool and can serve as a multi-purpose space for users. Almost any of Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup>‚Äôs products can be incorporated into of a pool house. One of Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup>'s glazed structures can be used as a free standing pool house, or any operable door or window system can be added to a conventional construction pool house to enhance function and aesthetics.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="2/3"][vc_single_image image="37280" img_size="full"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<h2><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37287" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/pool-house.png" alt="" width="680" height="400" /></h2>
<h2>Entertaining Space</h2>
A pool house can create a unique entertaining space. The implementation of a pool house allow you to keep the party out of the house and contained to the area surrounding the pool, but provide a conditional space. Instead of people tracking water and debris into your house after swimming, they can utilize the pool house for drinks, food, or a changing room or rest room. Including a bedroom and bathroom to a pool house (if the budget permits) is always an added bonus ‚Äì not only will this increase your home‚Äôs value, it will also provide you with a private area for visiting guests, away from the main living area.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_column_text]
<h2><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-37288" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/pool-house-stack-walls.png" alt="" width="680" height="400" /></h2>
<h2>WINDOW &amp; DOOR INTEGRATION</h2>
The addition of folding glass walls, slide and stack glass walls or sliding glass doors to the pool house allows for the walls to be opened to bring the ‚Äúpool inside,‚Äù and allows foot traffic to easily flow between the inside of the structure and the outside pool area. This also enables you to bask in the outdoor climate when the weather is pleasant. We also offer an array of specialty windows and doors along with decorative options to customize your pool house![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36920 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/multiple-styles-icon.png" alt="" width="107" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Multiple Styles</h2>
Solar Innovations<sup>¬Æ</sup> manufactures the highest quality glazed structures custom designed and engineered to match individual customer‚Äôs needs with a large variety of styles to choose from..[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/4"][vc_column_text]
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-36899 size-full" src="https://solarinnovations.com/wp-content/uploads/engineering-icon.png" alt="Custom Engineering for Custom Glazed Windows and Doors" width="120" height="102" /></h2>
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Custom Engineered</h2>
